_sText:
the map is simple there isn't much to it it. I wanted to create a fun gungame level that wouldnt just satisfy gameplay and Design although i use a small range of textures i try to make up for the Devs with Decals and Props laid out to create walls and Barriers and little focal points to look at.

i have tested it out with my friends and it is Good fun it is small simple and a very easy layout to get used to and with 2 main textures Design shouldnt be to distracting from actual gameplay. very fast paced and energetic.

This is my first 3D skybox which i just copied from the Sdk tutorial map as i had no idea what would look good with the Strange and weird world that icreated. so i thought that the obscure big buildings and walls would fit well.:D
